metadata.name: Lili rises #1
metadata.description:
'' And Lili, easy as a kiss we'll find an answer
Put all your fears back in the shade
Oh don't become a ghost without no colour
'Cause you're the best paint life ever made ''

U-Turn (Lili)
Song by AaRON

I chose a part of this song because my model name in these photos is Lili and Lili's life is similar to this song.
Lili has gone through a difficult period in her life and now she has put all her focus in life on her goal which is modeling . I know she will not go back to that time.
